### Corpse Tab

This feature monitors whether a corpse has spawned on your server, and when it does, it sends you a notification on Discord

**How to configure:**

1. In the **Corpse** tab, enter your **Discord Webhook** link in the designated field
2. Enter your **Discord User ID** to be mentioned in the message (optional)
3. Click **“Select Area”** and mark the region of the screen where the corpse spawn notification (IT APPEARS AGAIN) appears in the game
4. Activate the detector with the **Activate** button

**How to create a Webhook on Discord:**
1. Open the channel settings in Discord
2. Go to **Integrations → Webhooks → New Webhook**
3. Copy the link and paste it into JesterHub


